title: Schiff riding high amidst a fierce scramble for 2nd place in CA Senate race
description: A new POLITICO | Morning Consult poll reveals Rep. Adam Schiff as a clear leader in the race with Republican Steve Garvey and Democratic Reps. Katie Porter and Barbara Lee tied for second place.

title: The most unlikely ingredient to a successful career in Washington
description: Arthur Brooks ran the American Enterprise Institute for more than a decade. Now, he’s a fulltime happiness scientist. Here’s his guide to making it in Washington without sacrificing your humanity.
